Her notoriety generally stems from the shock that occurs when her long, foam-like flat breasts make their first appearance on webcam. They resemble a pair of clear gallon-size Ziplock bags that have been filled with Shit, piss and rotten [[furries]]. One can only imagine that the accompanying stench is comparable to [[Your mom|something akin to a steeping brew of Gummi Bears, human waste, Mountain Dew, and balsamic vinegar.]]

